"""Windows Win32 API + UI Automation handler.

v2.1.2 — Audit Round 4:
  #1 UIA: separate matching from traversal — children always visited
  #2 type_text: Unicode-only via KEYEVENTF_UNICODE (no VkKeyScanW for text)
  #3 SendInput: check returned insertion count — report failures
  #4 drag/hotkey/type: try/finally ensures mouse/key release on cancel
  #5 DPI: initialize_windows_runtime() called from both MCP + remote
  #6 Blocking ops → asyncio.to_thread for ImageGrab, UIA tree, registry, services
"""

